This subproject contains a version of Stan Birchfield's implementation 
of a Kanade-Lucas-Tomasi feature tracker that has been ported to OpenIMAJ 
by Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk).

The original implementation can be found here: http://www.ces.clemson.edu/~stb/klt/

As per the original code, the source code is in the public domain, available 
for both commercial and non-commercial use.

